    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/ea32024a40405d92292c7f6f23ccc3b2.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=800 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/ea32024a40405d92292c7f6f23ccc3b2.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/cdf9fdd667f00d384138233ced2fb951.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=612 height=265 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/cdf9fdd667f00d384138233ced2fb951.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/b1bc064adf1bceb1e45eb799bfa7dded.avif?t=1758893485\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras_big/b1bc064adf1bceb1e45eb799bfa7dded.avif?t=1758893485 width=800 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Splat Splat is a &quot;skill&quot; based top-down shooter 1v1 or 2v2 mayhem game! Splat your friend until they can't splat no more! Then do it again and again to become the ultimate Splatter! <br>Collect coins to bid for upgrades and gain advantage over your opponent!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/ece02f7850d0e0baacab4188736b4b40.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/ece02f7850d0e0baacab4188736b4b40.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/43dd23f2bf90ca90667aa4a15698b42b.avif?t=1758893485\" width=612 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/d58c26cae2aabe38a1b963e0712b42e8.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=200 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/d58c26cae2aabe38a1b963e0712b42e8.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/926faa7997f031e971e3c80bee0f2669.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=200 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/926faa7997f031e971e3c80bee0f2669.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/e272fcb231880925450e224c8b8b41c6.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=200 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/e272fcb231880925450e224c8b8b41c6.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Dynamic Arenas</strong> <br>Splat against your enemy in various dangerous battle arenas where only the strongest survive. Collect coins during battle while avoiding hazards to outsplat your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/7034828bcc5c690fec9d4175abf98462.avif?t=1758893485\" width=612 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/a09ccd0776ac3cf84aff355a82cc6a85.poster.avif?t=1758893485\" width=780 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/a09ccd0776ac3cf84aff355a82cc6a85.webm?t=1758893485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Use your coins</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Splatters earn coins during battles, these coins are used to bid against each other for powerful upgrades in the auction between rounds! <br> <br><strong>Upgrade your upgrades</strong> <br>Upgrades in the auction get more powerful for the underdog player, enabling comeback strategies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104920/extras/f7c1ad718e65523532e224ea280a571f.avif?t=1758893485\" width=612 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Splat Splat contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ &quot;Balanced&quot; Upgrade options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Dynamic Arenas </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local &amp; Online Multiplayer 1v1 or 2v2</p></li></ul>",
